      "author": "bjsi",
      "description": "Sorry for the long wait. Enjoy the new features and let me know if there are any issues!\r\n\r\n- Added: A modal to edit current repetition data - priority, next repetition date, interval, notes.\r\n- Fixed: Small simple scheduler and AFactor scheduler bugs.\r\n- Refactored: Bulk add links and notes to queue.\r\n- Added: Bulk add block references within note to queue.\r\n- Added setting: Set a default first repetition date for modals.\r\n- Fixed: Status bar bugs.\r\n- Added: Priority number to status bar.\r\n- Added: Smart add notes to queue by creating a mapping between tags and queue names.\r\n- Added: Optionally add a custom block ref name when adding a block to a queue.\r\n- Added: Optional inbox processing - set next repetition date and priority when you press next repetition.\r\n- Added: Next repetition and manually schedule next rep command.",
